WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
Anna and the Fighter by Elizabeth Laird

00:31.000 --> 00:34.000
Anna did not sleep all night.

00:34.000 --> 00:36.000
She was excited.

00:36.000 --> 00:39.000
Early in the morning her father called her.

00:39.000 --> 00:42.000
Come on Anna, it's time to get up.

00:42.000 --> 00:45.000
It's a long way to the station.

00:45.000 --> 00:48.000
Anna got dressed and she was soon ready.

00:48.000 --> 00:50.000
She did not eat any breakfast.

00:50.000 --> 00:52.000
She was nervous.

00:52.000 --> 00:55.000
She was going to visit her aunt in Nara.

00:55.000 --> 00:59.000
She was going alone in a train for the first time.

00:59.000 --> 01:04.000
Anna and her father left the village and began to walk to the station.

01:04.000 --> 01:07.000
It was a long way.

01:07.000 --> 01:10.000
They reached the station at midday.

01:18.000 --> 01:20.000
Soon the train came.

01:20.000 --> 01:22.000
It was nearly empty.

01:22.000 --> 01:23.000
Anna got in.

01:23.000 --> 01:25.000
She was frightened.

01:25.000 --> 01:29.000
It was her first journey away from home.

01:29.000 --> 01:31.000
Your aunt will meet you at Nara.

01:31.000 --> 01:33.000
Her father said.

01:33.000 --> 01:35.000
Be careful now Anna.

01:35.000 --> 01:38.000
Don't talk to any strangers.

01:47.000 --> 01:51.000
The train started suddenly.

01:51.000 --> 01:54.000
Soon it was going fast.

01:54.000 --> 01:56.000
Anna watched her father.

01:56.000 --> 01:58.000
He looked smaller and smaller.

01:58.000 --> 02:00.000
Then he disappeared.

02:04.000 --> 02:07.000
The train journey was very long.

02:07.000 --> 02:09.000
Anna looked out of the window.

02:09.000 --> 02:14.000
The fields, trees, villages and animals rushed past.

02:14.000 --> 02:18.000
After a long time she began to feel sleepy.

02:18.000 --> 02:21.000
She was very tired.

02:21.000 --> 02:24.000
Slowly she fell asleep.

02:24.000 --> 02:26.000
Later Anna woke up.

02:26.000 --> 02:28.000
It was dark outside.

02:28.000 --> 02:31.000
She felt small and lost.

02:31.000 --> 02:35.000
She was a long way from her village and her father.

02:35.000 --> 02:38.000
There was a man in the carriage with her now.

02:38.000 --> 02:43.000
He had an ugly face and he was very big and strong.

02:43.000 --> 02:46.000
His hair was very short.

02:46.000 --> 02:50.000
He looked bad and dangerous.

02:50.000 --> 02:52.000
The man smiled at Anna.

02:52.000 --> 02:53.000
Hello?

02:53.000 --> 02:54.000
He said.

02:54.000 --> 02:57.000
You're awake now are you?

02:57.000 --> 02:59.000
Where are you going?

02:59.000 --> 03:02.000
Anna remembered her father's words.

03:02.000 --> 03:05.000
She did not say anything.

03:05.000 --> 03:07.000
Are you going to Polona?

03:07.000 --> 03:09.000
Asked the man.

03:09.000 --> 03:11.000
Anna was surprised.

03:11.000 --> 03:12.000
No.

03:12.000 --> 03:13.000
To Nara.

03:13.000 --> 03:14.000
She said.

03:14.000 --> 03:15.000
Nara?

03:15.000 --> 03:17.000
Said the man.

03:17.000 --> 03:20.000
But we passed Nara two hours ago.

03:20.000 --> 03:25.000
You were asleep.

03:25.000 --> 03:27.000
Anna wanted to cry.

03:27.000 --> 03:29.000
She sat very still.

03:29.000 --> 03:33.000
It was warm in the carriage but Anna felt cold.

03:33.000 --> 03:36.000
We passed Nara?

03:36.000 --> 03:37.000
She asked.

03:37.000 --> 03:38.000
Yes.

03:38.000 --> 03:40.000
Said the man.

03:40.000 --> 03:43.000
Anna thought of the journey back to Nara.

03:43.000 --> 03:45.000
How much did it cost?

03:45.000 --> 03:48.000
She did not have any money.

03:48.000 --> 03:51.000
She thought of her aunt at Nara's station.

03:51.000 --> 03:53.000
Don't worry.

03:53.000 --> 03:54.000
Said the man.

03:54.000 --> 03:55.000
I'll help you.

03:55.000 --> 03:57.000
What's your name?

03:57.000 --> 03:58.000
Anna.

03:58.000 --> 03:59.000
She said.

03:59.000 --> 04:01.000
My name is Sam.

04:01.000 --> 04:03.000
Said the man.

04:03.000 --> 04:05.000
You can trust me Anna.

04:05.000 --> 04:08.000
Anna looked at Sam again.

04:08.000 --> 04:11.000
He was very ugly.

04:11.000 --> 04:14.000
He had a long scar on his face

04:14.000 --> 04:17.000
and he looked dangerous.

04:17.000 --> 04:20.000
But he seemed kind.

04:20.000 --> 04:23.000
Was he good or bad?

04:23.000 --> 04:25.000
Anna did not know.

04:25.000 --> 04:28.000
The train began to slow down.

04:28.000 --> 04:31.000
Sam got up and looked out of the window.

04:31.000 --> 04:34.000
Anna saw a newspaper on Sam's seat.

04:34.000 --> 04:37.000
There was a photograph on the back page.

04:37.000 --> 04:40.000
It was Sam's photograph.

04:40.000 --> 04:43.000
Above the photograph was a headline.

04:43.000 --> 04:48.000
This man is a dangerous fighter.

04:48.000 --> 04:50.000
Now Anna was sure.

04:50.000 --> 04:54.000
Sam was a bad man and dangerous too.

04:54.000 --> 04:56.000
He was a criminal.

04:56.000 --> 04:59.000
Anna must be careful.

04:59.000 --> 05:02.000
She must get away from him quickly.

05:02.000 --> 05:04.000
Sam left the window.

05:04.000 --> 05:06.000
We're coming into Polona now.

05:06.000 --> 05:07.000
He said.

05:07.000 --> 05:09.000
Stay with me.

05:09.000 --> 05:11.000
I'll help you.

05:11.000 --> 05:13.000
The train stopped.

05:13.000 --> 05:16.000
Anna jumped up and ran to the door.

05:16.000 --> 05:18.000
She wanted to run away.

05:18.000 --> 05:20.000
The door was very heavy.

05:20.000 --> 05:22.000
She could not open it.

05:22.000 --> 05:25.000
Sam was standing behind her.

05:25.000 --> 05:28.000
I'll open it, he said.

05:32.000 --> 05:37.000
At the station exit, Anna was stopped.

05:37.000 --> 05:39.000
Where's your ticket?

05:39.000 --> 05:42.000
This ticket is for Nara.

05:42.000 --> 05:44.000
I fell asleep.

05:44.000 --> 05:46.000
I passed Nara.

05:46.000 --> 05:49.000
I haven't got any money.

05:49.000 --> 05:50.000
I'll pay.

05:50.000 --> 05:52.000
Said a voice.

05:52.000 --> 05:54.000
It was Sam.

05:54.000 --> 05:56.000
Thank you, sir.

05:56.000 --> 05:58.000
Come with me, Anna.

06:04.000 --> 06:08.000
Anna wanted to run away, but she was frightened of Sam.

06:08.000 --> 06:11.000
She was tired and lost.

06:11.000 --> 06:13.000
Polona was a big town.

06:13.000 --> 06:16.000
Anna did not know anybody there.

06:16.000 --> 06:18.000
Sam called a taxi.

06:18.000 --> 06:20.000
Get in, Anna.

06:20.000 --> 06:21.000
He said.

06:21.000 --> 06:23.000
Anna got in.

06:23.000 --> 06:25.000
The boxer hotel.

06:25.000 --> 06:27.000
Sam said to the driver.

06:27.000 --> 06:29.000
The taxi went a long way.

06:29.000 --> 06:33.000
The streets of Polona were wide and busy.

06:33.000 --> 06:37.000
There were lots of cars and shops and people.

06:37.000 --> 06:42.000
The taxi turned into a small dark street and stopped.

06:42.000 --> 06:45.000
Sam got out and paid the taxi driver.

06:45.000 --> 06:48.000
Anna looked up and down the street.

06:48.000 --> 06:50.000
Come on, Anna.

06:50.000 --> 06:51.000
Said Sam.

06:51.000 --> 06:54.000
Anna could not run away.

06:54.000 --> 06:56.000
She was weak and slow.

06:56.000 --> 06:59.000
Sam was big and strong.

06:59.000 --> 07:02.000
She followed Sam into the hotel.

07:02.000 --> 07:05.000
There was a cafe inside the hotel.

07:05.000 --> 07:08.000
It did not look very clean.

07:08.000 --> 07:11.000
Two men were drinking and playing cards.

07:11.000 --> 07:13.000
They saw Sam.

07:13.000 --> 07:16.000
One of them said, hello, Sam.

07:16.000 --> 07:18.000
Come and have a drink.

07:18.000 --> 07:20.000
Who's the pretty girl?

07:20.000 --> 07:23.000
Sam took off his coat and sat down.

07:23.000 --> 07:25.000
Hello, Tina.

07:25.000 --> 07:26.000
Hello, Bubs.

07:26.000 --> 07:28.000
He said, this is Anna.

07:28.000 --> 07:30.000
She's lost.

07:30.000 --> 07:33.000
The men looked at Anna and laughed.

07:33.000 --> 07:35.000
Lost is she?

07:35.000 --> 07:36.000
Said Tina.

07:36.000 --> 07:38.000
Poor Anna.

07:38.000 --> 07:40.000
You're a lucky man, Sam.

07:40.000 --> 07:42.000
Have a drink.

07:44.000 --> 07:47.000
Sam gave Anna a chair.

07:47.000 --> 07:49.000
She sat down.

07:49.000 --> 07:51.000
She looked at the men.

07:51.000 --> 07:53.000
Tina had a mustache.

07:53.000 --> 07:56.000
Bubs did not have any front teeth.

07:56.000 --> 07:58.000
They looked tough.

07:58.000 --> 08:00.000
The men were drinking.

08:00.000 --> 08:03.000
Tina gave Anna a glass.

08:03.000 --> 08:04.000
Come on, Anna.

08:04.000 --> 08:07.000
He said, drink some wine.

08:07.000 --> 08:10.000
Anna pushed the glass away.

08:10.000 --> 08:14.000
She thought, I mustn't eat or drink anything.

08:14.000 --> 08:17.000
These men will give me a drug.

08:17.000 --> 08:19.000
Then I will fall asleep.

08:19.000 --> 08:21.000
Sam called the waiter.

08:21.000 --> 08:23.000
Bring some dinner.

08:23.000 --> 08:26.000
He said, bring some good hot food.

08:26.000 --> 08:29.000
The waiter came with the food.

08:29.000 --> 08:33.000
Bubs put some of the food on a plate and gave it to Anna.

08:33.000 --> 08:36.000
It looked good and smelt delicious.

08:36.000 --> 08:40.000
Anna forgot about drugs and began to eat.

08:40.000 --> 08:43.000
She ate quickly and finished everything.

08:43.000 --> 08:45.000
She put her spoon down.

08:45.000 --> 08:47.000
The men were looking at her.

08:47.000 --> 08:49.000
They laughed.

08:49.000 --> 08:52.000
Anna was very frightened again.

08:52.000 --> 08:53.000
Come on, Anna.

08:53.000 --> 08:54.000
Said Sam.

08:54.000 --> 08:56.000
You're tired.

08:56.000 --> 08:58.000
You must go to bed now.

08:58.000 --> 09:00.000
He took her arm.

09:00.000 --> 09:02.000
Lock her door, Sam.

09:02.000 --> 09:03.000
Said Tina.

09:03.000 --> 09:06.000
They're a bad man in Polona.

09:06.000 --> 09:08.000
You must keep her safe.

09:08.000 --> 09:10.000
Bubs laughed.

09:10.000 --> 09:12.000
Good night, Anna.

09:12.000 --> 09:14.000
He said.

09:16.000 --> 09:20.000
Sam took Anna upstairs and into a bedroom.

09:20.000 --> 09:22.000
Her heart was beating fast.

09:22.000 --> 09:24.000
Good night, Anna.

09:24.000 --> 09:25.000
Said Sam.

09:25.000 --> 09:27.000
He smiled at her.

09:27.000 --> 09:29.000
Don't worry.

09:29.000 --> 09:31.000
You're safe here.

09:31.000 --> 09:33.000
Anna did not say anything.

09:33.000 --> 09:39.000
Sam seemed kind, but she remembered the newspaper.

09:39.000 --> 09:44.000
Sam was dangerous and his friends looked dangerous too.

09:44.000 --> 09:47.000
She must escape.

09:47.000 --> 09:50.000
Sam went out of the room and shut the door.

09:50.000 --> 09:53.000
He locked it and went downstairs.

09:53.000 --> 09:57.000
Anna sat on the bed and cried.

10:02.000 --> 10:06.000
Downstairs the men drank and played cards.

10:06.000 --> 10:08.000
Anna heard their voices.

10:08.000 --> 10:10.000
They were laughing.

10:10.000 --> 10:14.000
After a long time, she fell asleep.

10:24.000 --> 10:27.000
Anna woke late.

10:27.000 --> 10:29.000
The sun was shining.

10:29.000 --> 10:31.000
She looked out of the window.

10:31.000 --> 10:34.000
The waiter was sitting outside in the street.

10:34.000 --> 10:38.000
He was smoking a cigarette and reading a newspaper.

10:38.000 --> 10:40.000
Anna looked around the room.

10:40.000 --> 10:42.000
It was dirty.

10:42.000 --> 10:45.000
There was some old paper on the floor.

10:45.000 --> 10:50.000
In one corner, there was a small table with some things on it.

10:50.000 --> 10:52.000
Anna had an idea.

10:52.000 --> 10:54.000
There was a baro on the table.

10:54.000 --> 10:59.000
She took the baro and picked up a piece of paper from the floor.

10:59.000 --> 11:04.000
She wrote, please help me.

11:04.000 --> 11:08.000
I want to go to NARA.

11:08.000 --> 11:11.000
My aunt is waiting for me there.

11:11.000 --> 11:14.000
I must escape from here.

11:14.000 --> 11:19.000
I have no money and no friends.

11:20.000 --> 11:22.000
Anna.

11:24.000 --> 11:27.000
She threw the note out of the window.

11:27.000 --> 11:29.000
The waiter picked it up.

11:29.000 --> 11:31.000
He read the note.

11:31.000 --> 11:33.000
He looked up and saw her.

11:33.000 --> 11:38.000
He smiled at her and went into the hotel.

11:39.000 --> 11:43.000
Anna heard voices outside her room.

11:43.000 --> 11:46.000
Somebody unlocked the door.

11:46.000 --> 11:48.000
The waiter came in.

11:48.000 --> 11:51.000
There was somebody on the stairs behind him.

11:51.000 --> 11:54.000
It's a policeman, thought Anna.

11:54.000 --> 11:57.000
He's brought a policeman.

11:57.000 --> 11:59.000
She ran forward.

11:59.000 --> 12:01.000
It was Sam.

12:01.000 --> 12:05.000
He was holding her note in his hand.

12:05.000 --> 12:07.000
Good afternoon, Anna.

12:07.000 --> 12:08.000
Said Sam.

12:08.000 --> 12:10.000
You've slept very late.

12:10.000 --> 12:12.000
You must be hungry.

12:12.000 --> 12:14.000
Come and have some food.

12:14.000 --> 12:16.000
We're going soon.

12:16.000 --> 12:19.000
The waiter smiled at Sam.

12:19.000 --> 12:21.000
Anna understood.

12:21.000 --> 12:24.000
The waiter did not want to help her.

12:24.000 --> 12:28.000
He and Sam were friends.

12:28.000 --> 12:31.000
Anna went downstairs with Sam and the waiter.

12:31.000 --> 12:34.000
They gave her some food, but she was not hungry.

12:34.000 --> 12:38.000
She did not eat or drink anything.

12:38.000 --> 12:41.000
Sam went outside into the street.

12:41.000 --> 12:43.000
Anna heard voices.

12:43.000 --> 12:46.000
Sam was talking to a man.

12:46.000 --> 12:48.000
What were they planning?

12:48.000 --> 12:50.000
Sam came inside again.

12:50.000 --> 12:53.000
Come on, Anna. We must go now.

12:53.000 --> 12:57.000
He said, a taxi was waiting outside.

12:57.000 --> 13:00.000
Anna and Sam got in.

13:00.000 --> 13:02.000
Where are we going?

13:02.000 --> 13:04.000
Anna asked.

13:04.000 --> 13:06.000
Sam looked at her.

13:06.000 --> 13:08.000
I'll take you to your aunt later.

13:08.000 --> 13:12.000
He said, first I have an important job to do.

13:12.000 --> 13:14.000
Sam smiled.

13:14.000 --> 13:17.000
The smile twisted his face.

13:17.000 --> 13:21.000
He looked very ugly.

13:21.000 --> 13:23.000
Soon the taxi stopped.

13:23.000 --> 13:26.000
Sam and Anna got out.

13:26.000 --> 13:28.000
They were outside a big building.

13:28.000 --> 13:32.000
There was a notice outside the building.

13:32.000 --> 13:41.000
Today, at three o'clock, Sam the fighter versus Danny the tiger.

13:41.000 --> 13:58.000
Anna understood now.

13:58.000 --> 14:01.000
Sam was a boxer.

14:01.000 --> 14:05.000
Dangerous fighter meant good boxer.

14:05.000 --> 14:08.000
Sam was not a criminal.

14:08.000 --> 14:11.000
Anna followed Sam into the building.

14:11.000 --> 14:13.000
It was a very big hall.

14:13.000 --> 14:16.000
There were seats on all sides.

14:16.000 --> 14:19.000
In the middle was the boxing ring.

14:19.000 --> 14:22.000
Tino and Bubs were waiting for them.

14:22.000 --> 14:24.000
Stay here, Anna.

14:24.000 --> 14:25.000
Said Sam.

14:25.000 --> 14:27.000
Tino and Bubs will look after you.

14:27.000 --> 14:30.000
I must go now.

14:30.000 --> 14:34.000
Tino and Bubs shook Sam's hand.

14:34.000 --> 14:36.000
Good luck, Sam.

14:36.000 --> 14:37.000
Said Bubs.

14:37.000 --> 14:40.000
You'll win all right, said Tino.

14:40.000 --> 14:44.000
Anna smiled at Sam for the first time.

14:44.000 --> 14:49.000
Good luck, Sam, she said.

14:49.000 --> 14:53.000
Tino and Bubs took Anna to a seat beside the ring.

14:53.000 --> 14:58.000
Tino sat on one side of her and Bubs on the other.

14:58.000 --> 15:00.000
Anna sat quietly and waited.

15:00.000 --> 15:05.000
The two men talked excitedly.

15:06.000 --> 15:09.000
Sam's going to win, said Tino.

15:09.000 --> 15:11.000
Of course he'll win.

15:11.000 --> 15:12.000
Said Bubs.

15:12.000 --> 15:15.000
He's the best fighter in the country.

15:15.000 --> 15:16.000
Anna listened.

15:16.000 --> 15:19.000
Sam was famous.

15:19.000 --> 15:21.000
Everybody wants him to win.

15:21.000 --> 15:22.000
Said Tino.

15:22.000 --> 15:24.000
Everybody likes him.

15:24.000 --> 15:25.000
That's right.

15:25.000 --> 15:26.000
Said Bubs.

15:26.000 --> 15:31.000
Sam's a great boxer and he's a good man too.

15:32.000 --> 15:35.000
I know a story about Sam, said Tino.

15:35.000 --> 15:39.000
One night he was asleep in bed.

15:39.000 --> 15:42.000
He heard shouts in the street and he looked outside.

15:42.000 --> 15:44.000
A house was on fire.

15:44.000 --> 15:46.000
He ran outside.

15:46.000 --> 15:49.000
There was a child in the burning house.

15:49.000 --> 15:53.000
He went inside and saved the child.

15:53.000 --> 15:55.000
But he was badly hurt.

15:55.000 --> 15:59.000
His face was burned and he got a bad scar.

15:59.000 --> 16:01.000
Poor Sam, said Bubs.

16:01.000 --> 16:03.000
That's why he's so ugly.

16:03.000 --> 16:06.000
They both laughed.

16:06.000 --> 16:08.000
Anna was listening quietly.

16:08.000 --> 16:11.000
She now understood everything.

16:11.000 --> 16:13.000
She was safe with Sam.

16:13.000 --> 16:16.000
She felt sorry for him.

16:16.000 --> 16:18.000
Is the fight going to start soon?

16:18.000 --> 16:20.000
She asked Tino.

16:20.000 --> 16:21.000
Yes, of course.

16:21.000 --> 16:22.000
Said Tino.

16:22.000 --> 16:26.000
It will start very soon.

16:27.000 --> 16:29.000
The hall was full of people now.

16:29.000 --> 16:32.000
Boys were selling cigarettes and sweets.

16:32.000 --> 16:35.000
Everybody was laughing and joking.

16:35.000 --> 16:37.000
The referee was waiting in the ring.

16:37.000 --> 16:40.000
The audience was excited now.

16:40.000 --> 16:45.000
Sam, Sam, we want Sam, they shouted.

16:45.000 --> 16:48.000
Sam climbed into the ring.

16:48.000 --> 16:52.000
He was wearing short trousers and big boxing gloves.

16:52.000 --> 16:55.000
He raised both hands in the air.

16:56.000 --> 16:58.000
The crowd was clapping.

16:58.000 --> 17:02.000
Sam, Sam, Sam, they shouted.

17:02.000 --> 17:05.000
The other fighter climbed into the ring.

17:05.000 --> 17:07.000
He was very big and strong.

17:07.000 --> 17:09.000
Here comes Danny.

17:09.000 --> 17:10.000
Said Tino.

17:10.000 --> 17:13.000
He's a very good fighter.

17:13.000 --> 17:15.000
Anna was worried.

17:15.000 --> 17:18.000
Don't you worry, Anna?

17:18.000 --> 17:19.000
Said Bubs.

17:19.000 --> 17:23.000
Sam's the best fighter in the country.

17:24.000 --> 17:28.000
The referee called the two boxers to the center of the ring.

17:28.000 --> 17:31.000
He spoke to them quietly for a few moments.

17:31.000 --> 17:34.000
Then Sam and Danny shook hands.

17:34.000 --> 17:39.000
The two fighters went back to their corners and waited.

17:39.000 --> 17:43.000
A bell rang and the fight began.

17:43.000 --> 17:51.000
Danny was younger than Sam.

17:52.000 --> 17:54.000
But he was a good fighter.

17:54.000 --> 17:56.000
He moved fast.

17:56.000 --> 18:01.000
He tried to hit Sam, but Sam jumped away every time.

18:01.000 --> 18:03.000
Sam's arms were long.

18:03.000 --> 18:05.000
He moved very quickly.

18:05.000 --> 18:10.000
He hit Danny hard many times.

18:10.000 --> 18:12.000
Anna was very excited.

18:12.000 --> 18:15.000
Her hands held the seat tightly.

18:15.000 --> 18:17.000
It was a long fight.

18:17.000 --> 18:19.000
Sam moved quickly.

18:19.000 --> 18:21.000
He hit Danny often.

18:21.000 --> 18:24.000
But Danny did not fall down.

18:24.000 --> 18:26.000
Sam was getting tired.

18:26.000 --> 18:29.000
He was moving more slowly.

18:29.000 --> 18:31.000
Anna was worried.

18:31.000 --> 18:33.000
The crowd was shouting.

18:33.000 --> 18:34.000
Sam!

18:34.000 --> 18:35.000
Sam!

18:35.000 --> 18:36.000
Anna shouted.

18:36.000 --> 18:37.000
Sam!

18:37.000 --> 18:38.000
Sam!

18:38.000 --> 18:39.000
Come on Sam!

18:39.000 --> 18:41.000
Watch out!

18:41.000 --> 18:44.000
Tino and Bubs were shouting too.

18:44.000 --> 18:47.000
Danny hit Sam's face hard.

18:47.000 --> 18:52.000
Blood came out of Sam's nose and one of his eyes was nearly closed.

18:52.000 --> 18:55.000
But Sam did not stop.

18:55.000 --> 19:02.000
He ran forward and hit Danny with all his strength.

19:02.000 --> 19:05.000
Danny fell over and lay still.

19:05.000 --> 19:08.000
The referee started to count.

19:08.000 --> 19:13.000
One, two, three, four.

19:13.000 --> 19:15.000
Danny did not move.

19:15.000 --> 19:19.000
Five, six, seven.

19:19.000 --> 19:21.000
Danny tried to get up.

19:21.000 --> 19:22.000
He could not.

19:22.000 --> 19:28.000
Eight, nine, ten.

19:28.000 --> 19:30.000
Danny lay still.

19:30.000 --> 19:32.000
The fight was over.

19:32.000 --> 19:35.000
Sam was the winner.

19:35.000 --> 19:38.000
Anna was laughing and clapping.

19:38.000 --> 19:40.000
Well done Sam!

19:40.000 --> 19:42.000
Well done Sam!

19:43.000 --> 19:44.000
Nobody heard her.

19:44.000 --> 19:46.000
Everybody was shouting.

19:46.000 --> 19:47.000
Sam!

19:47.000 --> 19:48.000
We want Sam!

19:48.000 --> 19:50.000
We want Sam!

19:56.000 --> 19:59.000
Tino and Bubs took Anna to the dressing room.

19:59.000 --> 20:01.000
Sam was resting.

20:01.000 --> 20:03.000
Hello Sam!

20:03.000 --> 20:04.000
Said Anna.

20:04.000 --> 20:06.000
You were great.

20:06.000 --> 20:08.000
Sam was surprised.

20:08.000 --> 20:10.000
Hello Anna.

20:10.000 --> 20:13.000
He said, you're different now.

20:13.000 --> 20:18.000
You didn't talk to me before.

20:18.000 --> 20:20.000
I'm sorry Sam.

20:20.000 --> 20:21.000
Said Anna.

20:21.000 --> 20:24.000
I was frightened.

20:24.000 --> 20:25.000
I know.

20:25.000 --> 20:27.000
Said Sam.

20:27.000 --> 20:31.000
I'm big and ugly and you were frightened.

20:31.000 --> 20:34.000
But I'm not a criminal Anna.

20:34.000 --> 20:36.000
I'm sorry Sam.

20:36.000 --> 20:38.000
Anna said again.

20:38.000 --> 20:40.000
I was wrong.

20:40.000 --> 20:42.000
I'm not frightened now.

20:42.000 --> 20:44.000
Sam was pleased.

20:44.000 --> 20:46.000
Come on Anna.

20:46.000 --> 20:49.000
He said, we'll go to Nara now.

20:49.000 --> 20:52.000
Your aunt is waiting for you.

20:52.000 --> 20:55.000
Anna said goodbye to Tino and Bubs.

20:55.000 --> 20:57.000
She got into a taxi with Sam.

20:57.000 --> 21:00.000
It was a long way to Nara.

21:00.000 --> 21:03.000
And Anna asked Sam many questions.

21:03.000 --> 21:06.000
They talked and talked and talked.

21:06.000 --> 21:09.000
They reached Nara at night.

21:09.000 --> 21:11.000
It was dark.

21:11.000 --> 21:12.000
Sam knew Nara.

21:12.000 --> 21:15.000
He quickly found Anna's aunt's house.

21:15.000 --> 21:17.000
They knocked on the door.

21:17.000 --> 21:19.000
The door opened.

21:19.000 --> 21:22.000
Anna's aunt was standing in the doorway.

21:22.000 --> 21:24.000
She was crying.

21:24.000 --> 21:26.000
Oh Anna.

21:26.000 --> 21:27.000
Anna.

21:27.000 --> 21:31.000
She said, thank God you are here at last.

21:31.000 --> 21:33.000
Then she saw Sam.

21:33.000 --> 21:35.000
He looked terrible.

21:35.000 --> 21:39.000
His face was cut and bruised after the fight.

21:39.000 --> 21:40.000
Anna.

21:40.000 --> 21:43.000
She said, who is this man?

21:43.000 --> 21:44.000
Auntie.

21:44.000 --> 21:47.000
Anna said, don't be angry.

21:47.000 --> 21:49.000
This is Sam.

21:49.000 --> 21:51.000
I fell asleep on the train.

21:51.000 --> 21:54.000
I passed Nara station.

21:54.000 --> 21:56.000
Sam helped me.

21:56.000 --> 21:58.000
He took me to a hotel.

21:58.000 --> 22:01.000
He brought me to Nara in a taxi.

22:01.000 --> 22:04.000
Anna's aunt looked at Sam again.

22:04.000 --> 22:06.000
Wait a minute.

22:06.000 --> 22:09.000
She said, she ran inside.

22:09.000 --> 22:12.000
She came back with a newspaper.

22:12.000 --> 22:16.000
Sam's photograph was on the back page.

22:16.000 --> 22:19.000
Are you Sam the boxer?

22:19.000 --> 22:20.000
She asked.

22:20.000 --> 22:22.000
Yes I am.

22:22.000 --> 22:24.000
Said Sam.

22:24.000 --> 22:26.000
Anna's aunt was pleased.

22:26.000 --> 22:28.000
Sam was famous.

22:28.000 --> 22:30.000
He was a great man.

22:30.000 --> 22:32.000
Everybody knew him.

22:32.000 --> 22:34.000
Come in Sam.

22:34.000 --> 22:37.000
She said, please sit down.

22:37.000 --> 22:40.000
Will you have some tea?

22:40.000 --> 22:43.000
Anna sat in the room with her aunt and Sam.

22:43.000 --> 22:45.000
She did not say anything.

22:45.000 --> 22:48.000
She felt very happy.

22:48.000 --> 22:51.000
Anna's aunt asked Sam many questions.

22:51.000 --> 22:53.000
She laughed a lot.

22:53.000 --> 22:56.000
She liked him.

22:56.000 --> 22:58.000
It was getting very late.

22:58.000 --> 23:00.000
I must go now Anna.

23:00.000 --> 23:02.000
Said Sam.

23:02.000 --> 23:04.000
Can I come and see you again?

23:04.000 --> 23:06.000
Yes Sam.

23:06.000 --> 23:08.000
Said Anna.

23:08.000 --> 23:10.000
She smiled at him.

23:30.000 --> 23:50.000
Anna and the fighter was read by Kate Harper and the recording produced by James Richardson at Studio AVP London.

